### Amusement parks and rides

For those who crave thrills beyond the roll of the dice, the [Strip](/Las_Vegas_Strip) offers a surprising array of amusement park attractions. The [Adventuredome](/Adventuredome), an indoor amusement park nestled within [Circus Circus](/Circus_Circus_Las_Vegas) on the [Strip](/Las_Vegas_Strip), stands as a major tourist draw. [89] Enclosed within a sprawling glass dome, it features a carousel, mini-golf, two roller coasters, bowling, various spinning rides, an arcade, virtual reality experiences, a carnival midway, and, of course, clown shows. [89]

The towering [Stratosphere](/Stratosphere_Las_Vegas) (now simply [The Strat](/The_Strat)) offers a collection of extreme rides perched precariously atop its spire:

